imdb.plot outline: The One (2011) and The One (2008) is an Australian 'reality' TV show based on the idea that some people have psychic or supernatural powers. Each show put the contestants, who claim to have such powers, to a series of tests. Each show see the eminination of one or more of the contestants until only three are left. The winner is then decided by a phone poll from viewers.
